					<a class="block px-7 py-5 w-full h-full whitespace-nowrap" href="#">部落格</a></li>
				<li
					class="hover:bg-gl-dark-red ease-in-out duration-300 border-0 -sm:mx-auto w-1/2 -sm:border border-gl-dark-red text-center">
