				</ul>
				<ul
					class="social flex right:0 -sm:w-auto -sm:relative t-0 -sm:right-[-20px] -xxs:right-[-36px] -xxs:w-full">
					<li>
						<a href="">
							<img src="https://github.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/blob/main/week3-4/ic-social-fb.png?raw=true"
								alt="facebook">
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="">
							<img src="https://github.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/blob/main/week3-4/ic_social_ig.png?raw=true"
